    接口 说明
    CancelToastInput
    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module toaster input; The schema path to identify an instance is toaster/cancel-toast/input To create instances of this class use CancelToastInputBuilder.
    CancelToastOutput
    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module toaster output; The schema path to identify an instance is toaster/cancel-toast/output To create instances of this class use CancelToastOutputBuilder.
    FrozenBagel
    Frozen bagel.
    FrozenWaffle
    Frozen waffle.
    HashBrown
    Hash browned potatos.
    MakeToastInput
    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module toaster input { leaf toasterDoneness { type uint32 { range "1 .. 10"; } default 5; } leaf toasterToastType { type identityref { base toast:toast-type; } default wheat-bread; } } The schema path to identify an instance is toaster/make-toast/input To create instances of this class use MakeToastInputBuilder.
    MakeToastOutput
    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module toaster output; The schema path to identify an instance is toaster/make-toast/output To create instances of this class use MakeToastOutputBuilder.
    RestockToasterInput
    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module toaster input { leaf amountOfBreadToStock { type uint32; } } The schema path to identify an instance is toaster/restock-toaster/input To create instances of this class use RestockToasterInputBuilder.
    RestockToasterOutput
    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module toaster output; The schema path to identify an instance is toaster/restock-toaster/output To create instances of this class use RestockToasterOutputBuilder.
    Toaster
    Top-level container for all toaster database objects.
    ToasterData
    YANG version of the TOASTER-MIB.
    ToasterListener
    Interface for implementing the following YANG notifications defined in module toaster notification toasterRestocked { leaf amountOfBread { type uint32; } } notification toasterOutOfBread { }
    ToasterOutOfBread
    Indicates that the toaster has run of out bread.
    ToasterRestocked
    Indicates that the toaster has run of out bread.
    ToasterService
    Interface for implementing the following YANG RPCs defined in module toaster rpc make-toast { input { leaf toasterDoneness { type uint32 { range "1 .. 10"; } default 5; } leaf toasterToastType { type identityref { base toast:toast-type; } default wheat-bread; } } output; } rpc cancel-toast { input; output; } rpc restock-toaster { input { leaf amountOfBreadToStock { type uint32; } } output; }
    ToastType
    Base for all bread types supported by the toaster.
    WheatBread
    Wheat bread.
    WhiteBread
    White bread.
    WonderBread
    Wonder bread.
